"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Hello. This is the original (and currently the only) **[NODEMONS](https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/28587048870449139916496856695809964505895964223150990494805643042180290314241)**[ NFT drop](https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/28587048870449139916496856695809964505895964223150990494805643042180290314241).\\n\\n**NODEMONS** is two things. It is an entirely new set of original short stories set in the shared fantasy world of the Golden Realms.\\n\\n**NODEMONS** is also a new type of publishing house; one which uses the blockchain and enthusiasm of fans to fund, develop, and co-own pieces of art and fiction.\\n\\nWe’re nearly ready to enter the Golden Realms in our first short story series. More on that soon. Until then we are celebrating with a brand new NFT drop of our mascot - Yasumi - a mischievous punk demon, formed through the combination of unholy magic from the fetid bones of early tech and crypto capitalists. Lost in their greed - their souls warmed only by the exhausts of their mining rigs - and resurrected with the dark magic manifested from the frustration of lost wallet passwords, Yasumi represents our enthusiasm for the power of blockchain, while recognizing and embracing it’s counter-cultural origins and destiny. Oh yeah.\\n\\n![Yasumi says kon'nichiwa.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Y5BRp8zVN22qNBG0Kr31v.jpg?height=1224&width=792)\\n\\n[Buy now. Invest. Yasumi wants you to.](https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/28587048870449139916496856695809964505895964223150990494805643042180290314241)\\n\\n\\\\--\\n\\nNODEMONS recognizes that while the blockchain can operate in a carbon neutral way in the fullness of time, it does not do so today. We offset the energy of our blockchain gas with donations to sustainable energy non-profits. Our 2022 charity is Mayan Power and Light; you can learn more on Global Giving.\",\